why:
data ecience: Simplifying data exploration and axplanation in data science.
Business/Marketing: Identifying health metrics and disease spread in healthcare.
Healthcare: Monitoring health metrics and disease spread in healthcare/
Finance: Analysing stock prices and financial performance in finance.
education: Tracking student performance over time in education.

